OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter serious assault
OL,6,FA 34-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith attempted murder after another
OL,8,Fman was found with serious injuries in
OL,9,Fsouth Bristol.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,12,Fresidential property in Whitchurch on
OL,13,FSaturday, 28 March, following reports
OL,14,Fof an incident at the address.
OL,16,FAvon and Somerset Police said a man in
OL,17,Fhis 60s was found with serious
OL,18,Finjuries inside the property, and he
OL,19,Fremains in hospital.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
