OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter serious assault
OL,6,FThomas Gwyther, from Hengrove, has
OL,7,Fbeen charged with attempted murder and
OL,8,Fappeared before Bristol Magistrates'
OL,9,FCourt on Monday 30 March.
OL,11,FHe has been remanded in custody to
OL,12,Fappear at Bristol Crown Court on 6 May.
OL,14,FThe force said a woman, in her 60s,
OL,15,Fwho was arrested over the weekend has
OL,16,Fbeen released on bail pending further
OL,17,Fenquiries.
